          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/19/157749474/c369b96fc6417e8fc2bb607e37297ad4_4176113773608719444.png",
                "id": "talent53000",
                "key": "迴身箭术",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "迴身箭术"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素伤害</span>，本角色附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">疾风示现</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">疾风示现</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附属角色进行重击时：</span>少花费1个<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">无色元素</span>，造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>变为<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素伤害</span>，并且使目标角色附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">风压坍陷</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/19/157749474/6f3f1e66aac8d91ecca768d4a7f48e56_4757002501140762526.png",
                "id": "talent55926",
                "key": "非想风天",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "非想风天"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素伤害</span>，召唤<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">赫耀多方面体</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/19/157749474/bec3c6e3c0067cc3e0340d50df63f27e_6789877573027318729.png",
                "id": "talent90254",
                "key": "抟风秘道",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "抟风秘道"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：3</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">此召唤物在场时：</span>敌方角色受到的<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素伤害</span>+1。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/19/157749474/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_9189341656256418639.png",
                "id": "talent29063",
                "key": " 赫耀多方面体",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/19/157749474/7c29f5ce38f0d332fbd3113f1b605a5c_9076938779292301532.png",
                "title": " 赫耀多方面体"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附着的元素发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（冰）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点冰伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（水）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点水伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（火）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点火伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（雷）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点雷伤害</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/19/157749474/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_4536683029280960874.png",
                "id": "talent46199",
                "key": "风元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "风元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">重击</span></strong></p><p>我方行动开始前，如果元素骰总数为偶数，则进行的「普通攻击」将被视为「重击」。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">无色元素</span></strong></p><p>可以用任意类型的元素骰子组合，来支付此类费用。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">风压坍陷</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>将所附属角色切换为「出战角色」。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：1</span></p><p>（同一方场上最多存在一个此状态）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: white\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: white\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/19/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_691209927560464542.png",
